OL,3,CBritish funerals increasingly
OL,4,C'celebrations of life', study finds
OL,6,FBritish funerals are increasingly
OL,7,Fbecoming "celebrations of life" marked
OL,8,Fby personal touches rather than sombre
OL,9,Fand traditional services, according to
OL,10,Fa study.
OL,12,FSome 68% of people believe funerals
OL,13,Fshould be more of a celebration than a
OL,14,Ftime of reflection, up from 58% in
OL,15,F2019, the study by Co-op Funeralcare
OL,16,Ffound.
