OL,3,CBritish funerals increasingly
OL,4,C'celebrations of life', study finds
OL,6,FThe study, largely based on
OL,7,Finformation from more than 500,000
OL,8,Ffunerals carried out by Co-op
OL,9,FFuneralcare's funeral directors over
OL,10,Fthe last five years, highlights a
OL,11,Ftrend towards more personalised
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FMore than half of the funeral
OL,15,Fdirectors (53%) said they are seeing a
OL,16,Fmove away from tradition and an
OL,17,Fincrease in people wanting a unique
OL,18,Fservice that reflects the deceased's
OL,19,Flife.
