OL,3,CBritish funerals increasingly
OL,4,C'celebrations of life', study finds
OL,6,FRequests have ranged from from Dr Who-
OL,7,Fthemed farewells and glittered
OL,8,Fcoffins, to mourners dressed in
OL,9,Ffootball shirts.
OL,11,FAlmost six in 10 funeral directors
OL,12,F(57%) reported an increase in requests
OL,13,Ffor services to take place outside
OL,14,Ftraditional religious settings, while
OL,15,Falmost half of those surveyed (48%)
OL,16,Fsaid they had attended a funeral in a
OL,17,Fnon-traditional setting over the last
OL,18,Fyear.
