OL,4,C'celebrations of life', study finds
OL,6,FThree-quarters (75%) had received
OL,7,Frequests for pets to attend the
OL,8,Ffuneral, while 62% of people surveyed
OL,9,Fsaid it is important that pets are
OL,10,Fable to attend their owner's service.
OL,12,FAlmost a third of funeral directors
OL,13,F(31%) said they have seen people
OL,14,Fposting on social media from a
OL,15,Ffuneral, while almost a fifth (18%)
OL,16,Fhave seen people taking selfies.
