OL,6,FSentimental items placed inside a
OL,7,Fcoffin over the last five years have
OL,8,Fincluded cigarettes and a mobile
OL,9,Fphone, bingo items and a snooker cue,
OL,10,Ffuneral directors reported.
OL,12,FGill Stewart, managing director at Co-
OL,13,Fop Funeralcare, said: "Since our
OL,14,Fprevious report in 2019, many factors
OL,15,F` including the pandemic ` have made
OL,16,Fpeople think about the subject of
OL,17,Fdeath and funerals much more.
