OL,3,CBritish funerals increasingly
OL,4,C'celebrations of life', study finds
OL,6,F"With this new report, we want to
OL,7,Fencourage the nation to talk to their
OL,8,Floved ones about their funeral wishes,
OL,9,Fwhether that be putting plans in place
OL,10,For even discussing a favourite song
OL,11,Fchoice.
OL,13,F"Whilst it can feel daunting, it can
OL,14,Fhelp make an otherwise difficult time
OL,15,Fthat little bit easier if plans are
OL,16,Fknown or in place for when they're
OL,17,Fneeded."
OL,19,F` Opinion Matters surveyed 4,002 UK
OL,20,Fadults between May 31 and June 4.
